{
  "stem": "5883.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they brought them to one place where was already-- a grave was already digged out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And before they started shooting, he-- the soldier didn't look.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He crawled away into the bushes, and he saw with his own eyes his parents get killed with his sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he wandered from city to city, farm, farm till finally he find that place where to stay.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- and then he asked my mother if she wouldn't mind not to adopt him and change his name, because he would like to carry on his own name.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother, you know, she told him, fine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You've got your wish, and he stayed with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then he find a uncle in Chicago, and he left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "At that time, I was already here in Washington.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he left for his uncle, and he was in touch with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He would let us know that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he didn't like the way his uncle was treating him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He wrote me a letter one day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He wanted to come back and be with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I said, fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he lived together with us till he got married.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he treated my mother and father just like his own parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very strange.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything looked, you know, funny to you because you were away from the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, everything was like you just were born.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was very hard to get used to back to normal life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the houses were empty because most of the houses which were empty were Jewish houses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we walked in one house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was furniture.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a bed, you know, table and-- so I really give credit, most of it, to my mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was a very strong woman, a very good woman.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
